{"id": "7aecad97-a0d9-431a-ac6b-36ae9dbfaf38", "task_id": "eed4ecfe-509b-4661-817a-df0cb6919d0e", "path": "backend/templates/index.html", "artifact_type": "file", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Cyberpunk Login</title>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <style>\n        /* General Body Styling */\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; /* Futuristic monospaced font */\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a0a2a 50%, #0a0a0a 100%); /* Dark, moody gradient */\n            color: #00ffc0; /* Neon green-blue */\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        /* Glitch effect background (subtle) */\n        body::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-image: url(\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='6' height='6' viewBox='0 0 6 6' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='%2300ffc0' fill-opacity='0.05' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cpath d='M0 0h3v3H0V0zm3 3h3v3H3V3z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E\"); /* Subtle pixel/grid pattern */\n            opacity: 0.2;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            z-index: -1;\n            animation: background-pan 60s linear infinite; /* Slow background movement */\n        }\n\n        @keyframes background-pan {\n            from {\n                background-position: 0% 0%;\n            }\n            to {\n                background-position: 100% 100%;\n            }\n        }\n\n        /* Container for the login form */\n        .login-container {\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); /* Semi-transparent dark background */\n            border: 2px solid #00ffc0; /* Neon border */\n            box-shadow: 0 0 30px #00ffc0, 0 0 60px #8a2be2; /* Dual neon glow */\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n            max-width: 400px;\n            width: 90%;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            position: relative;\n            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        /* Title styling */\n        .login-container h1 {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; /* Aggressive, futuristic font */\n            color: #ff00ff; /* Magenta neon */\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff00ff, 0 0 20px #ff00ff, 0 0 30px #00ffff; /* Triple neon glow */\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .login-container h1::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 50%;\n            bottom: -10px;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 3px;\n            background: #ff00ff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 8px #ff00ff, 0 0 16px #00ffff;\n            border-radius: 2px;\n        }\n\n        /* Form group for labels and inputs */\n        .form-group {\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            text-align: left;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .form-group label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            color: #00ffff; /* Cyan neon */\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 5px #00ffff;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .form-group input[type=\"text\"],\n        .form-group input[type=\"password\"] {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px 15px;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n            border: 1px solid #00ffff; /* Cyan border */\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            color: #00ffc0; /* Neon green-blue text */\n            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.4);\n            transition: border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Important for padding/width calculation */\n        }\n\n        .form-group input[type=\"text\"]:focus,\n        .form-group input[type=\"password\"]:focus {\n            border-color: #ff00ff; /* Magenta on focus */\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.6), 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.4);\n            outline: none;\n        }\n\n        /* Placeholder text style */\n        .form-group input::placeholder {\n            color: rgba(0, 255, 192, 0.5); /* Faded neon placeholder */\n        }\n\n        /* Submit Button */\n        .submit-button {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background-color: #00ffc0; /* Neon green-blue button */\n            color: #1a0a2a; /* Dark text for contrast */\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px #00ffc0, 0 0 30px #00ffff;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n        }\n\n        .submit-button:hover {\n            background-color: #00ffff; /* Cyan on hover */\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px #00ffff, 0 0 40px #ff00ff;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        .submit-button:active {\n            transform: translateY(0);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px #00ffff, 0 0 20px #ff00ff;\n        }\n\n        /* Message area for Jinja2 feedback */\n        .message {\n            color: #ff00ff; /* Magenta for error/success messages */\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 5px #ff00ff;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 600px) {\n            .login-container {\n                padding: 30px;\n                margin: 20px;\n            }\n\n            .login-container h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n\n            .form-group label {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n\n            .form-group input[type=\"text\"],\n            .form-group input[type=\"password\"] {\n                padding: 10px 12px;\n            }\n\n            .submit-button {\n                padding: 12px;\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"login-container\">\n        <h1>LOGIN // SYSTEM</h1>\n        {% if error_message %}\n            <p class=\"message\">{{ error_message }}</p>\n        {% endif %}\n        <form action=\"/login\" method=\"POST\">\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\n                <label for=\"username\">USERNAME:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"username\" name=\"username\" placeholder=\"Enter your username\" required>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\n                <label for=\"password\">PASSWORD:</label>\n                <input type=\"password\" id=\"password\" name=\"password\" placeholder=\"Enter your password\" required>\n            </div>\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"submit-button\">ACCESS // SYSTEM</button>\n        </form>\n    </div>\n    <script>\n        // No custom JavaScript functionality is required by the task.\n        // The form submission is handled by standard HTML POST request.\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n", "patches": [], "metadata": {"language": "html", "framework": "static_html", "explanation": "This Jinja2 template (`index.html`) provides a cyberpunk-themed login form. It uses inline CSS for styling, featuring a dark background, neon glow effects for text and form elements, and futuristic fonts imported from Google Fonts. The form uses standard HTML attributes (`action=\"/login\"`, `method=\"POST\"`) for submission, ensuring compatibility with a backend FastAPI application. A Jinja2 conditional (`{% if error_message %}`) is included to display potential error messages from the server, enhancing the user experience without requiring client-side JavaScript for form validation blocking submission. Minimal vanilla JavaScript is included as a placeholder, though no complex JS logic is currently needed per the task's focus on HTML/CSS.", "dependencies": []}, "created_at": "2026-06-17 16:26:08.164694"}